snippet.title: Best VGM 850 - Killer Instinct - The Instinct (Main Theme)
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

SNES / Gameboy / N64
Killer Instinct (1995)
The Instinct (Main Theme)
Robin Beanland & Graeme Norgate
